<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4675318>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 2. Chalaraspidum alatum [SIO 60-243]. (A) Posterior end of the labrum (posterior is up), ventral view. Labrum tooth (lt) with ‘hook’. (B) Armature of the ‘hook’. (C) Left mandible, view on the edge with incisor process (ip), lacinia mobilis (lm), cusp c (cc) and molar process (mp). (D) Left mandible, posterior view. (E) Right mandible, view on the edge. (F) Right mandible, anterior view. Between incisor and molar process, cusps b (cb) and c (cc). There is a notch between the two cusps (arrow). (G) Left paragnath, anterior view, ventral is up, right paragnath (rp) on the right side. (H) Left paragnath, ventral view, anterior is up; maxillula (mx 1) posterior of paragnath." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4675318/files/figure.png" .

